	(Attach_Node_To_Collection): New procedure.
	(Detach_Node_From_Collection): Likewise.
	(Finalization_Started): Likewise.
	(Finalize): New overriding procedure.
	(Header_Size): New function.
	(Initialize): New overriding procedure.
